msgid "KDE Linux"
msgstr "KDE Linux"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.linux.metainfo.xml:9
msgid ""
"A modern Linux distribution focused on the KDE Plasma desktop environment"
msgstr ""
"Un moderne distribution de Linux focalisate sur ambiente de scriptorio "
"Plasma de KDE"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.linux.metainfo.xml:14
msgid ""
"KDE Linux is a user-friendly operating system built around the KDE Plasma "
"desktop environment. It provides a complete computing experience with a "
"focus on productivity, customization, and ease of use."
msgstr ""
"KDE Linux es un systema operative (o operational) facile a usar construite "
"circa le ambiente de scriptorio de KDE Plasma. Il forni un complete "
"experientia computational con un foco sur productivitate, personalisation, e "
"facilitate de uso."

